## 🇨🇦 Description (EN-CA)

This repository explores the power of the C programming language through essential structures:

- **Pointers**: direct memory manipulation and referencing  
- **Vectors**: dynamic data allocation and access  
- **Matrices**: multidimensional logic and mathematical operations  

> Inspired by the logic of the gods and the precision of warriors, this C collection is part of our Valhalla educational arc – a noble tribute to structured programming.

